details: Order #78421 created for US agent dataset scrape
Start payment released (non-refundable once work begins)
200-row sample CSV uploaded for format confirmation
Buyer confirms headers/date format acceptable; reminds acceptance criteria apply to final set
Buyer reports: duplicates above threshold; many blank city/state; contactability below 60%; provides examples
Seller offers to remove duplicates and re-export but disputes contactability requirement; asks to release final milestone
Updated CSV uploaded; no updated source_domains.csv; buyer states still below coverage/contactability
Buyer opens dispute to withhold 3000 LOB acceptance milestone
Seller requests release of Acceptance milestone
